{"id": "1401092370375774228", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 19, "author_id": "173543218573606913", "author_name": "madoor", "author_bot": false, "content": "uvhash: (probably) the shortest one but has a really interesting dynamic between uvhash and the keeper (or technically the person they're inhabiting in the dream)\n\nagrippa: kind of silly shenanigans between agrippa and the keeper with an ending i didnt like too much, also doesn't solely focus on her backstory. honestly feel like the uvhash/agrippa dreamscape does a better job of exploring her character. \n\ntulu: probably the best one imo, kind of feels like a mini dreamscape as its a bit longer than the others and has the keeper taking a very passive role. felt like tulu was a much more interesting/complicated character after reading it.\n\nliz: touches on some pretty dark themes that normally wouldn't be explored in morimens. not a particularly complicated story but the writing is effective and compelling.", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T06:40:52.135000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1401083240152039547", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
